divs: Sighting Detailswas sitting on porch and i noticed a v shaped object although it looked like it had several compartments that were attached it was white or maybe gray , couldent tell if it was emitting light or blocking light.thought it might have been birds but there wasnt any flapping motions.was fairly large heading west.seemed to be going much faster that birds would have been.lost sight of it due to a roof.and there were two wittnesess we both agreed of what we saw and did discuss it for awhile before reporting it.
